Package soot.jimple.infoflow.android.resources

Class ARSCFileParser

  • java.lang.Object
    • soot.jimple.infoflow.android.resources.AbstractResourceParser
      • soot.jimple.infoflow.android.resources.ARSCFileParser
  • public class ARSCFileParser
extends AbstractResourceParser
    Parser for reading out the contents of Android's resource.arsc file. Structure declarations and comments taken from the Android source code and ported from C to Java.
    Author:
    Steven Arzt
